{"tid":2501416,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加國參議員豪沙科斯：我們必須實施制裁和向勇敢挑戰中共政權的香港人提供庇護","createTime":"2021-04-23T10:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T11:36:49.000Z","uid":70063,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"91ae9c9e19de9de63bb612f37f37598eed725a0e","tid":2501416,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:46:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenatorHousakos/status/1383411956887871490?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorHousakos%2Fstatus%2F1383411956887871490%3Fs%3D19&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzqg2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=e04018e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorHousakos%2Fstatus%2F1383411956887871490%3Fs%3D19&h=8e621408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenatorHousakos/status/1383411956887871490?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenatorHousakos/status/1385227527535349766?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorHousakos%2Fstatus%2F1385227527535349766%3Fs%3D19&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzqg2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=5438d0f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorHousakos%2Fstatus%2F1385227527535349766%3Fs%3D19&h=6564c000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenatorHousakos/status/1385227527535349766?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"fc683ad5fc7181db0e2b82d35433bdaf1718cc80","tid":2501416,"uid":80303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"腐敗的帝國儘管開始時掌握了常備軍、首都、官僚體系和看得見的GDP和物質資產，而蠻族那一方則好像是什麼也沒有，<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">當初1956年和1920年逃到西方的那些匈牙利人和俄羅斯人，當初從柏林大學逃到西柏林去建立自由大學的那批德國人，看上去都是一無所有，<br />\n<br />\n他們除了自己的頭腦和雙手以外什麼都沒有，大學留下的資本都被共產黨人佔有了，<br />\n<br />\n但是幾十年以後，他們的頭腦和雙手為他們在西方無中生有地重新創造了一個新世界，</span><br />\n<br />\n而佔有了過去地主資本家全部財富的無產階級卻把這些財富糟蹋得乾乾淨淨，<span class=\"red\">結果蘇聯還是倒下了</span>。<br />\n<br />\n帝國的故事也是這樣的。羅馬帝國和秦漢帝國最終都逃不了專制消滅創造力和生產力的必然命運；而那些逃到蠻族部落去，願意過美國拓荒者一樣的艱苦生活，放棄了聖彼得堡、布達佩斯和柏林原有的高級知識分子和達官貴人的富裕生活，像美國紅脖子一樣從頭做起的人，最終變成了他們的征服者。"},{"pid":"bf8124d5b768360ceff975d5e6b31c85d94b95bf","tid":2501416,"uid":300006,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T11:01:40.000Z","msg":"唔好庇護，可唔可以炸鳩北京"},{"pid":"e15c87d389b782f26bfaa6d57000ad6f6301a99e","tid":2501416,"uid":80303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf8124d5b768360ceff975d5e6b31c85d94b95bf","tid":2501416,"uid":300006,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T11:01:40.000Z","msg":"唔好庇護，可唔可以炸鳩北京"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T11:36:49.000Z","msg":"加拿大<br />\ndon't ff too much"}]}